consensus text: The opinion opposite to yours, is the
most rational, the most easily defended,
the most consistent with the true spirit
of the christian religion [insertion]*[/insertion] are perfectly
intelligible; these should be made the
Basis of our faith. These will bear
the test of Reason, these will stand
will exist as long as Man exists.
By these I mean the Unity of God, the necessity of Morality
and future state of retributions founded on the Resurrection.
